text: Nash Bridges is an American police procedural television series. It was created by Carlton Cuse. The show stars Don Johnson and Cheech Marin as two inspectors with the San Francisco Police Department's Special Investigations Unit (SIU). ==Other websites== * Category:1996 American television series debuts Category:2001 American television series endings Category:1990s American drama television series Category:1990s crime television series Category:2000s American drama television series Category:2000s crime television series Category:American crime television series Category:CBS network shows Category:Television series set in Chicago Category:English- language television programs
